                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "So \"cheap\" is in terms of hardware cost? Or software as well?\nFrom what you say it sounds as if Android is a reasonable development platform by now. Are there any development tools you would recommend in particular?"
